import React from 'react';
import Header from './components/Heading/Header';
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, Link } from "react-router-dom";

const App = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Header />
      <Router>
        <Switch>
          <Route path='/about'>
            <About/>
            </Route>
          <Route path='/users'>
            <Users />
          </Route> 
          <Route path='/'>
            <Home />
          </Route> 
        </Switch>
      </Router>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
